<div type="content"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_188_r1l13"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . Als vns ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> von 
<add><ab facs="#facs_188_line_1577089632040_1422"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Amman<ex>n</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l14"><expan>Tumh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒu Eyſtet etc vnd <expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> Bayrs <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>B<ex>urgers</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l15">wegen <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd darauff auch derſelb her <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l16">ſein rede vor vns gen dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> ercʒelet / Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l17">Davvider derſelb ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>geantvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> hat / vvie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l18">daʒ Er <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> nye ıchts ſchuldig <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan> ſey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l19">oder gelten ſülle . <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein pruder hans <expan>Amman<ex>n</ex></expan> der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l20">vorcʒeiten <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> . geweſen vnd ein ley iſt hab Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l21">vormals hıe vor gericht <expan>cʒugeſproch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von 
<del rend="strikethrough"> gelt </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l22"><expan>etlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> geltſchulde wegen als Er mainet / die der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l23"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> ~ <expan>ſein<ex>er</ex></expan> wirtin ſchuldig wer / darümb Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l24">der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> mit <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> rehten <expan>eınproch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſey / Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l25">darüber ſo hab derſelb <expan>han<ex>n</ex>s</expan> Amman <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_188_r1l26"><expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> pruder <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſache <expan>beuolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> für geiſtlich </ab>
</del>
<pb facs="#facs_189" id="93v"/><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_189_r2l1">reht cʒu vvenden / Vnd vvir doch ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>meiſt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r2l2"><expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> / als der mit <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>obgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_line_1577089707854_1462">brief für vns kome vnd ſeın rede ercʒelt / von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_line_1577089730288_1474">wegen ſagen vnd pẏeten lieſſen / Ob Er cʒu dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r2l7"><expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> icht <expan>cʒuſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> het / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r2l8"><expan>beſund<ex>er</ex></expan> von <expan>ſölch<ex>er</ex></expan> gelt ſchuld vnd <expan>werltlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> ſache </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r2l9">wegen / daʒ wir Jm darümb <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒoge<ex>n</ex>s</expan> ſleunigs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r2l10">rehten <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> helffen wolten vor des Reychs Rıhter </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r2l11">cʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> / Daran Er ſich niht benügen <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> noch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r2l12">gekert hat / vnd hat <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> den <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r2l13">Burger für geiſtlıch gerihte gewendet / Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_line_1577089780528_1505">maint Jn damit <expan>vmbcʒetreẏb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd ʒubeſweͣren </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_line_1577089785983_1510"><expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> ſıch der ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> damit niht behelffen kan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r2l18">das vns von <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> vnglimpflich </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r2l19">vnd vnbillich dunkt Vnd hoffen 
<del rend="strikethrough">auch </del> daʒ eʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_line_1577089843033_1566"><expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> auch niht glimpflich <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> billich </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_line_1577089849650_1571">dunk / noch Jm des cʒulegen oder <expan>geſtate<ex>n</ex></expan> wölle </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_line_1577089856881_1576">hyrümb <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> . daʒ Jr den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> geruchet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_line_1577089863487_1581">daran cʒuvveiſen / daʒ Er von <expan>ſölch<ex>er</ex></expan> klag auff </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r2l28"><expan>geiſtliche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan> laſſe / Vnd reht von ~ <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_189_r2l29">hier vor des Reichs <expan>Rıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> neme </ab>
